parsed.explanation: The XML was corrected for several structural and semantic issues. Specifically: 1. Two instances of improperly nested `<BIBL>` elements were identified where multiple titles by the same author were grouped incorrectly. These were split into distinct `<BIBL>` entries, each representing a separate work. 2. In one of the split entries, the content of a `<VOLUME>` tag ('8e Exempla politica') was merged into the `<TITLE>` tag, as it appeared to be part of the title rather than a volume number. 3. A typographical error was corrected, changing the tag `<PRICE>` to `<PRIZE>` to maintain consistency with other price tags in the document.
